0:01:20.680,0:01:27.380
iwe haugoni kumiririra Mwari, kuita mabasa aMwari pasina Mweya Mutsvene.

0:01:27.380,0:01:31.340
Uyo ano Muona anoona Mweya Mutsvene.

0:01:31.340,0:01:35.080
