Koniriyasi anodana Petirosi - Ndiri kungotora kuverenga kubva mundima 1.

0:04:59.340,0:05:07.240
PaKesaria pakanga pano mumwe murume ainzi Koniriasi,

0:05:07.240,0:05:19.120
mukuru wezana weHondo yavaItaria.

0:05:19.120,0:05:30.320
Iye nemhuri yake vakanga vakazvipira uye vaitya Mwari;

0:05:30.320,0:05:39.940
aipa kwazvo kuna vanoshayiwa uye ainyengetera kuna Mwari nguva dzose

0:05:39.940,0:05:48.580
Saka, ngatitorei chidzidzo chedu ipapo- ndima 44.

0:05:48.580,0:06:00.720
"Petirosi achiri kutaura mashoko aya, Mweya Mutsvene akauya pamusoro pavose vakanzwa shoko.

