kureva kuti vasingatendi; vanhu vavanga vasiri kutarisira kuti izvi zvingasvika kwavari, zvingadururwa pavari.

0:06:28.060,0:06:33.760
nokuti vakavanzwa vachitaura nedzimwe ndimi"

0:06:33.760,0:06:36.360
Tichazotaura pamusoro peizvi zvose nhasi.

0:06:36.360,0:06:40.540
"Nokuti vakavanzwa vachitaura ne dzimwe ndimi vachirumbidza Mwari. Ipapo Petirosi akati,

0:06:40.540,0:06:47.340
Kune munhu here angadzivisa mvura.

0:06:47.360,0:06:58.440
Sezvandakuudzai, rubhabhatidzo rwemvura nderwe chiito chemunhu; wongorora izvozvo.

0:06:58.440,0:07:03.060
"Ava vakapiwa Mweya Mutsvene sesu'.

0:07:03.060,0:07:08.460
Zvino akarayira kuti vabhabhatidzwe muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:07:08.460,0:07:16.700
Ipapo vakakumbira kwaari kuti ambogara mamwe mazuva. "

0:07:16.700,0:07:20.480
Sei Petirosi aifanira kugara navo kwemazuva mashoma?

0:07:20.480,0:07:25.360
Kuraira, kutungamira, nokuda kwechinangwa.

0:07:25.360,0:07:34.580
Mune ma Bhuku mazhinji pano nhasi, ayo achakubatsirai.

0:07:34.580,0:07:37.900
Hareruya. - Ameni.

0:07:37.900,0:07:42.860
Ma Kristu anofanira kuzadzwa neMweya Mutsvene.

0:07:42.860,0:07:51.020
Iwe unofanira kuzadzwa no Mweya Mutsvene kuti uve muKristu.

0:07:51.020,0:08:00.260
Hapana munhu anogona kuita basa raMwari asina Mweya Mutsvene.

0:08:00.260,0:08:23.560
Kuzviita usina Mweya Mutsvene kwakafanana nokutora kutambudzika kukuru, dambudziko, marwadzo.

0:08:23.560,0:08:32.520
Bhaibheri rinoti havasi vose vanoti "Jesu ndiye Ishe" vachaita zvinhu ne rubatsiro rwe Mweya Mutsvene.

0:08:32.520,0:08:36.440
Iwe unogona kutaura, kuita nekuparidza, pasina rubatsiro rwe Mweya Mutsvene

0:08:36.440,0:08:49.520
asi iwe uchaona kuti urikuunza marwadzo, maronda, kuzvikuvadza wega pachako.

0:08:49.520,0:08:52.160
Saka, ngatirevei zvakataurwa na Petirosi

0:08:52.160,0:09:06.140
Apo Petirosi akanga achitaura, Mweya Mutsvene wakawira pamusoro pevateereri.

0:09:06.140,0:09:10.880
Zvinorevei izvozvo?

0:09:10.880,0:09:20.120
Zvinoreva kuti wakawira pane avo vakatenda,

0:09:20.120,0:09:31.720
pane avo vakagadzirira Mweya Mutsvene,

0:09:31.720,0:09:46.720
zvinoreva kuti Mwari ndiye aiva muridzi wemashoko aPetirosi uye akatsigira mashoko aPetirosi.

0:09:46.720,0:09:52.800
Mune mamwe matsananguriro, akatumwa naMwari pachake.

0:09:52.800,0:10:02.600
Ndihwo umboo hunoratidza kuti akatumwa naMwari pachake.

0:10:02.600,0:10:11.240
Akanga asiri Petirosi - aiva mumiririri, nhume.

0:10:11.240,0:10:16.120
Ndichakutsananguriyai chimwe ne chimwe, sezvandakuudzai - ndichagoverana nemi kusangana kwangu neMweya Mutsvene,

0:10:16.120,0:10:17.840
kuti zvigova nyore kwamuri.

0:10:17.840,0:10:26.100
Kana ndichitaura pamusoro pezviri muBhaibheri chete, zvinogona kunge zvakaoma kwauri, asi ngatiende.

0:10:26.100,0:10:28.500
Hongu.

0:10:28.500,0:10:35.240
Kugadzirira Mweya Mutsvene - "Ndinoda kubhabhatidzwa, ndinoda chaizvo kuzadzwa noMweya Mutsvene."

0:10:35.240,0:10:37.440
Danho rauchatora:

0:10:37.440,0:10:43.280
Teerera kwandiri nemwoyo wako wese.

0:10:43.280,0:10:48.580
Unofanira kuteerera kwandiri ne chii chako chose? - Mwoyo.

0:10:48.580,0:11:00.200
Mwoyo unochengeta zvigumbu, mhosva, marwadzo ekare - ipapo ndipo panobva zvinetso zvako.

0:11:00.200,0:11:10.140
Munhu wose aripano ane mhaka imwe kana iyo yaanochengeta.

0:11:10.140,0:11:15.860
Kusakanganwira - munhu wese pano.

0:11:15.860,0:11:17.220
Vatariri, nditeererei:

0:11:17.220,0:11:22.160
Munhu wose anochengeta mhosva imwe kana iyo.

0:11:22.160,0:11:27.960
Iwe uri kudhimanda kodzero dzako, "Ndinga nyengedzwa, kunyombwa, sei?"

0:11:27.960,0:11:35.620
Hazvinei kuti unonyengedzwa kana kwete, chigumbu imhosva kuna Mwari.

0:11:35.620,0:11:44.760
Teerera kwandiri nemwoyo wako wese asi kwete mwoyo wakachengeta mhosva kana marwadzo ekare.

0:11:44.760,0:11:48.860
Asi iwe wakachengeta mhaka.

0:11:48.860,0:11:52.560
Muchiitiko chekudhimanda kodzero yako, uri kuchengeta zvigumbuso.

0:11:52.560,0:11:57.620
Ndicho chikonzero zvichave zvakaoma kuti iwe unzwe shoko rangu nemwoyo wako wose.

0:11:57.620,0:12:02.560
Iwe uchanzwa, iwe uchandiona ini semudzidzisi ...

0:12:02.560,0:12:07.140
Muchikoro unonzwa, asi zvinopinda mune chii?

0:12:07.140,0:12:09.940
Mupfungwa dzako?

0:12:09.940,0:12:13.600
Iwe unogamuchira asi kwete mumwoyo mako.

0:12:13.600,0:12:19.520
Kugamuchira shoko nemwoyo wako wose, mwoyo wako unofanira kuva wakasununguka.

0:12:19.520,0:12:22.800
Mwoyo zvinoreva mweya wemunhu.

0:12:22.800,0:12:28.700
Vangani vedu vane mwoyo wakasununguka pano nhasi?

0:12:28.700,0:12:38.440
Mwoyo usingachengete zvigumbu, kukanganisirwa, mwoyo usina chekuita nezvazuro,

0:12:38.440,0:12:43.760
hazvinei nezvakaitika, kunze kweizvo zvinopa rukudzo kuna Mwari.

0:12:43.760,0:12:47.780
Apa ndipo pauri!

0:12:47.780,0:12:54.860
Ndicho chikonzero zvichave zvakaoma kuti iwe undinzwe nemwoyo wako wose.

0:12:54.860,0:13:00.600
Ndiri kugoverana newe kuti unogona kubhabhatidzwa sei,

0:13:00.600,0:13:07.940
kuti unogona sei kuzadzwa neMweya Mutsvene.

0:13:07.940,0:13:11.540
Teerera!

0:13:11.540,0:13:22.540
Unofanira kunditeerera nemwoyo wako wese - mwoyo usingachengete mhosva.

0:13:22.540,0:13:33.880
Zvitaudze pachako muMapisarema mumwoyo mako pauri kunditeerera.

0:13:33.880,0:13:38.260
Hapana mwoyo usina kwawakarerekera. Iwe haugoni kuti, "Hm, ini handidi kutaura".

0:13:38.260,0:13:40.920
Kana iwe usingadi kutaura, mwoyo wako uchataura.

0:13:40.920,0:13:42.080
Chimwe chinhu chiri kuitika.

0:13:42.080,0:13:47.460
Usabvumira mweya wako kukutonga; ndiwe unoudzora.

0:13:47.460,0:13:53.280
"Ndinofanira kukudzora iwe." Pandiri kuterera kuna T.B. Joshua, ndinofanira kudzora mwoyo wangu. "

0:13:53.280,0:14:00.400
Zvitaudze pachako muMapisarema, nziyo nenziyo dzomweya,

0:14:00.400,0:14:04.480
imba nziyo mumwoyo mako kuna Mwari.

0:14:04.480,0:14:08.760
Asi mwoyo mingani ikozvino irikuita izvozvo ...?

0:14:08.760,0:14:11.020
Zvinhu zvakawanda zviri kuitika mumwoyo mako.

0:14:11.020,0:14:12.660
"Chii chichaitika nhasi?"

0:14:12.660,0:14:16.660
Usabvumira mwoyo wako kuti ukutonge.

0:14:16.660,0:14:23.080
Se muKristu, taura nemwoyo wako muMapisarema, nziyo ne nziyo dzomweya.

0:14:23.080,0:14:30.200
Imba dziyo mumwoyo mako. Ndiyo nzira yekugamuchira nayo.

0:14:30.200,0:14:36.660
Panguva yaunogona kubata mwoyo wako, wava pedyo ne kuzadzwa.

0:14:36.660,0:14:40.540
Haugoni kudzikamisa mwoyo wako; mwoyo wako uri kusvetuka svetuka.

0:14:40.540,0:14:46.200
Zvinhu zvakawanda zviri kuitika, "Bhizinesi rangu. Regai nditarise nguva yangu."

0:14:46.200,0:14:51.360
Ndicho chikonzero dzimwe nguva haufaniri kuenda kuchimbuzi, chirwere cheshuga chauri kutaura nezvacho.

0:14:51.360,0:14:53.840
Zvakadaro nokuti iwe hausi kudzora mwoyo wako.

0:14:53.840,0:14:57.020
Kana mwoyo wako uri kusvetuka svetuka, "Handina kuenda kuchimbuzi nhasi"

0:14:57.020,0:15:00.860
- pakarepo apo une pfungwa yekuenda kuchimbuzi.

0:15:00.860,0:15:05.860
"Handina kudya nhasi" - pakarepo wava ne pfungwa yekudya.

0:15:05.860,0:15:11.780
"Handina kufonera mukoma wangu nhasi" - pakarepo unogamuchira foni.

0:15:11.780,0:15:14.280
Hondo chaiyo iri mumwoyo yedu.

0:15:14.280,0:15:17.000
Kuwirirana - kusawirirana.

0:15:17.000,0:15:21.280
Kana ukagona kudzora mwoyo wako, kudzikamisa mwoyo wako, denga ndiro muganhu wako.

0:15:21.280,0:15:22.120
Udza agere pedyo newe,

0:15:22.120,0:15:28.760
Kana iwe ukakwanisa kudzora mwoyo wako, denga ndiro muganhu wako.

0:15:28.760,0:15:34.000
Ukasiya mwoyo wako; iwe uri kutarisa kwandiri asi mwoyo wako wakasununguka kutaura chero zvaunoda kutaura.

0:15:34.000,0:15:36.520
Usabvumira izvozvo!

0:15:36.520,0:15:41.660
Apo wakatarisa kwandiri, dzora mwoyo wako.

0:15:41.660,0:15:47.760
"Torai zvakawanda kwandiri, ndipei zvakawanda zvenyu, kutendeka kwenyu kwakawanda, mutsa, kunaka ..." -

0:15:47.760,0:15:53.820
zvakawanda zve Mapisarema eBhaibheri, nziyo, chuni.

0:15:53.820,0:15:58.340
"Jesu, Jesu ..." - izvozvo chete zvakakwana.

0:15:58.340,0:16:05.320
"Jesu, Jesu ..."

0:16:05.320,0:16:11.600
"Jesu, nenyasha dzenyu ndionei."

0:16:11.600,0:16:17.920
Ipa mwoyo wako basa.

0:16:17.920,0:16:22.100
Kana iwe ukasapa mwoyo wako chekuita, mwoyo wako uchatsvaga chekuita.

0:16:22.100,0:16:27.160
"O, tarisa magadzirirwo ebvudzi iro.Hona dhirezi iro.

0:16:27.160,0:16:32.460
Tarisa mudzimai akanaka uyo. Tarisa murume akanaka uyo.

0:16:32.460,0:16:38.620
Chechi ino - mune zvakawanda zvakachinja. O Mwari wangu."

0:16:38.620,0:16:41.220
Mwoyo wako uchange uchifamba-famba.

0:16:41.220,0:16:45.600
Kana iwe usingapi shoko kumwoyo wako, mwoyo wako uchange uchingoita chero chipi zvacho,

0:16:45.600,0:16:51.660
"Tarisa kune michero, ini ndichawana umwe here nhasi ?" Chii chichaitika? O, chechi ino yakanaka.

0:16:51.660,0:16:56.260
O, tarisai murume uyu; Ndinoda sutu yake - ndinofunga kuti ndinogona kuiwana.

0:16:56.260,0:17:04.020
Ndaona jipi imwe kunopakwa mota nhasi; Ndinofunga kuti ndichatora pikicha ye jipi yacho. "

0:17:04.020,0:17:09.100
Mwoyo wako unoramba uchifamba-famba; izvi ndizvo zviri kukupinza mumatambudziko.

0:17:09.100,0:17:11.280
Izvi ndizvo zvichakusudurudza kure na Mwari.

0:17:11.280,0:17:14.700
Ichi ndicho chikonzero nei usina kuzadzwa no Mweya.

0:17:14.700,0:17:16.540
Taura nemwoyo wako!

0:17:16.540,0:17:19.180
Mwoyo wako ngaugare uchishena shena; chengetedza mwoyo wako!

0:17:19.180,0:17:21.280
Uhu ndiwo hupenyu hwangu.

0:17:21.280,0:17:27.860
Pandinenge ndichienda, handitomboziva kuti uri kundipfuura, nokuti ndiri ku shena shena mumwoyo mangu.

0:17:27.860,0:17:34.560
Iwe unofunga kuti nokuti handisi kutaura handisi kushena shena - ndiri kushanda.

0:17:34.560,0:17:40.380
Dzimwe nguva, pandinoona TV, nhabvu ...

