0:18:02.380,0:18:06.940
Kana kuti pandinovata, hunhu hwangu ndehwe kurega mwoyo uchishanda

0:18:06.940,0:18:12.380
Ndinopa mwoyo wangu basa, kwete kuti mwoyo wangu undipe basa.

0:18:12.380,0:18:15.320
Mwoyo wako urikukupa basa.

0:18:15.320,0:18:20.680
Kana ndakarara - unofunga kuti ndakarara; muviri wangu chete.

0:18:20.680,0:18:21.920
Huya undirwise.

